# notes.md

> Per-swarm architecture and environment notes. This file is OPTIONAL.
> When present at `~/.hyvemind/swarms/<id>/notes.md`, its contents are
> injected into the Worker prompt under the `### Architecture & Environment
> Notes` subheader.
>
> This is the consolidated replacement for Factory's `library/architecture.md`,
> `library/environment.md`, and `library/user-testing.md` triplet --- one
> file, three optional sections.

